reviewText: GRANDAUGHTER LIKES IT BUT SHORT MOVIE SHOULD OF BEEN LITTLE LONGERSHE LIKE THE MCKIDS MADE IN 1998 SHE LOOKS AT THAT OVER AND OVER LOVES BUT SHE STILL LIKE SHOW SHE IS 2 1/2
This is a great video for children. They need to get back to having Ronald McDonald as the kids really enjoy him. Recommend.

My daughter really likes this movie.  It was one of her favorite christmas presents last year, since she had the other McKids movie.  She was so excited to get another.  I think she really likes it because it has real kids in it.  I've watched it with her and it's pretty good, better than a lot of cartoons.
